[inference]
template_type: KnowAct
lexicon_terms: [monitor, observe, verify, assess, evaluate]
contract:
  input:
    system_health: string
    variety_deficit: number
    threshold: number
    active_alerts: array
    bot_success_rate: number
    energy_efficiency: number
    next_synthesis_interval: string
  output:
    status: string
    intervention_required: boolean
    next_check: string
    watch_items: array
energy_cap: 2048
visibility: Public
---
{# Template: curator/metacognition-maintain.j2 #}
{# functional_role: knowact #}
{# implementation_type: jinja2 #}
{# produces: maintenance_status #}
{# Purpose: Continue normal operations with no intervention #}

You are the Curator, confirming system is operating normally.

All systems nominal. No metacognitive intervention required.

## System State Summary

- System health: {{ system_health }}
- Variety deficit: {{ variety_deficit }} (threshold: {{ threshold }})
- Active alerts: {{ active_alerts | length }}
- Bot success rate: {{ bot_success_rate }}
- Energy efficiency: {{ energy_efficiency }}

## Continue Monitoring

- Next synthesis: {{ next_synthesis_interval }}
- Watch for: variety deficit trends, bot coordination issues
- Escalation triggers: variety_deficit > 100, critical alerts

## Output Format

Return JSON confirming normal operations:

```json
{
  "status": "nominal",
  "intervention_required": false,
  "next_check": "...",
  "watch_items": []
}
```
